data.description: A fantastic opportunity awaits in beautiful Brookwood Crossing, near 21st and Cumberland Rd in Indy's east side.  3300+ sq ft comprise this lovely, well kept, and thoughtfully updated 5 bedroom/3 bathroom home nestled in a cul-de-sac of charming surroundings.  The home boasts a 3-car garage, and serene back patio with spacious backyard.  Virtually all big-ticket items updated recently, such as a new roof, HVAC, windows, counters, vinyl laminate flooring, and other custom touches throughout the home that make this home a star!  Stainless appliances, spacious bedrooms, and a primary bed/bath that would entice any exacting new owner.  Great kitchen prep space and butler cabinetry with granite counters, give the final classy element to tie everything together.  Updates listed on attached docs, room sizes are approximate.
